### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### 1. Create a new User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Mario",
  "lastName": "Rossi",
  "email": "mario.rossi@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "phone": "+391234567890",
  "roleId": 1
}

### 1. Login (Super Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@fiumicello.com",
  "password": "SuperSecretPassword123!"
}

### 2. Create User (Should be Guest)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "new.user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "roleId": 1 
}

### 3. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 4. Delete User (Soft Delete)
@userId = replace_with_uuid_from_response
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

### 5. Verify Soft Delete (Get User again - check isActive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
